  "description": "A close-up, ground-level view of a forest floor. The scene is filled with a mix of decaying leaves in shades of brown and orange, interspersed with vibrant green vegetation. A branch covered in bright orange lichen and patches of pale grey/white lichen lies horizontally across the frame, acting as a central feature. Small, delicate green plants with rounded leaves grow around the branch. The background consists of a scattering of leaf litter, twigs, and patches of moss. The overall texture is organic and varied, showcasing the natural decomposition and regrowth within a woodland habitat.",
